{"tid":657593,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳Comcast挑戰迪士尼 爭購霍士資產","createTime":"2018-05-08T08:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T14:19:36.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2f8e2b85ab4b17e5c520a55858e5bb05db48bb","tid":657593,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"美國最大有線電視集團Comcast 據報有意與迪士尼競爭，收購21世紀霍士（21st Century Fox ）資產。受消息刺激，21世紀霍士股價在延長交易時段最多升逾5%。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道，Comcast正與投資銀行洽談過渡貸款，以作全現金出價。此舉料將威脅迪士尼收購21世紀霍士電影及電視資產，價值520億美元的交易。<br />\n<br />\n若消息屬實，媒體巨頭收購戰的形勢將變得更多複雜。此前，Comcast 才挑戰霍士，出價220億英鎊（約300億美元），提出收購英國天空廣播（Sky） 。<br />\n<br />\n報道指述消息人士指，Comcast已經取得收購天空廣播的融資，並正要求投行增加過橋貸款的額度至最高600億美元，以應付收購霍士資產的資金。"},{"pid":"782071187c9ef15a46d64174f54fb12b1971967d","tid":657593,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"Comcast 即係環球？"},{"pid":"7fe631985dce799521e5634a6785568c6c273fed","tid":657593,"uid":185749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"782071187c9ef15a46d64174f54fb12b1971967d","tid":657593,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"Comcast 即係環球？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"環球係Universal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec55b6e4464d748c18d7a4217fcde4ad0df1567","tid":657593,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"782071187c9ef15a46d64174f54fb12b1971967d","tid":657593,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"Comcast 即係環球？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"Universal - A Comcast Company"},{"pid":"044ae5499ecfba831948c0117715bf35b0168327","tid":657593,"uid":66839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7ec55b6e4464d748c18d7a4217fcde4ad0df1567","tid":657593,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"782071187c9ef15a46d64174f54fb12b1971967